new_arrivals.title: New Arrivals
new_arrivals.description: Fresh out of the oven — hot new movies and shows just for you, added weekly!

300175.title: Stand Up Guys
300175.description: After one of them gets paroled, three retired gangsters reunite and reminisce as another ponders his next job — killing his old friend.

300839.title: Mystery Team
300839.description: A group of young detectives are challenged to crack a murder case and finally prove themselves as real detectives once and for all, in this comedy.

303190.title: The Usual Suspects
303190.description: The lone survivor of a heist-gone-wrong tells the feds how it all went down as they search for the enigmatic crime lord behind the disaster.

304773.title: Drugstore Cowboy
304773.description: Bob leads a family of junkies that rob drug stores for their fix. When a member dies, he goes straight. But not everyone is willing to let him leave.

308307.title: Buried
308307.description: Paul Conroy wakes up buried six feet underground with a lighter, a rapidly dying cell phone, low oxygen and no idea who put him there or why.

312183.title: Jeepers Creepers
312183.description: After making a horrific discovery in the basement of an old church, a pair of siblings find themselves the chosen prey of an indestructible force.

316454.title: Secretary
316454.description: Hoping to recover from her troubled past, a socially awkward woman becomes a secretary for an eccentric lawyer who is aroused by her obedience.

369730.title: Igby Goes Down
369730.description: Born into privilege, a rebellious teenager longs for a life far from his schizophrenic father, self-absorbed mother, and conservative big brother.

389507.title: Home of the Brave
389507.description: Three soliders return home after a traumatic experience in Iraq and find that living a normal life will be much more difficult than they thought.

389846.title: The Other End of the Line
389846.description: When a woman working at a call center in India falls for a man over the phone, she travels to San Francisco to see if it is true love after all.

390873.title: Blue State
390873.description: A fed-up Democrat hits the road to Canada with a mysterious traveling companion following the 2004 re-election of President George W. Bush.

396731.title: Song One
396731.description: Franny returns home when an accident leaves her brother comatose. Retracing his life as an aspiring musician, she tracks down his idol.

396732.title: Short Term 12
396732.description: Grace, a young supervisor at a foster care facility for at-risk teenagers, takes on the crises of two new residents while going through her own.

396741.title: Ink
396741.description: Father and daughter are thrust into a fantastical battle between forces of good and evil in this tale of love, loss and the search for redemption.

398629.title: The Woman in the Fifth
398629.description: After traveling to Paris only to be rejected by his estranged wife, a man strikes up an affair with a mysterious woman who may not be what she seems.

398765.title: Happythankyoumoreplease
398765.description: A sharp comedy centered on a group of 20-something New Yorkers struggling to figure out themselves, their lives, and their loves.

399691.title: Requiem for a Dream
399691.description: The lives of four people intertwine in this gut-wrenching, hypnotic tale of addiction and the devastation it has on their lives and those around them.

400842.description: A young British soldier is accidentally abandoned by his unit following a riot on the streets of Belfast in 1971, and must survive against the odds.

400846.title: The Rules of Attraction
400846.description: Based on the darkly satirical novel, three college students navigate an unconventional romantic triangle amidst sex, drugs and rock ‘n’ roll.

400849.title: Sunshine Cleaning
400849.description: A once-popular single mother-turned-maid gets a new lease on life when she gets into the lucrative world of crime scene cleanup with her sister’s help.

401468.title: Undertow
401468.description: In a contemporary South untouched by time, two brothers run away from home following their father’s death to guard a secret from their greedy uncle.

401471.title: The Dark Half
401471.description: A precocious writer undergoes a grotesque operation which reveals a twin in his brain.  He begins a double writing life, using his real name on "art" novels and using a pseudonym for his disreputable best-sellers.  When the pseudonym discovers he is to be eradicated by public acknowledgment, he goes on a murderous rampage--leaving all of the evidence pointed at the writer.

401473.title: City of Ghosts
401473.description: After fleeing the investigation of an insurance scam in the United States. Jimmy Cremming discovers his partner and mentor Marvin has surfaced in Cambodia, and sets off to get his promised cut of the action.

404566.title: The Adventures of Priscilla, Queen of the Desert
404566.description: For three drag-queen showgirls, a four-week engagement in Australia was the dream of a lifetime, but getting there intact may be a huge drag.

404579.title: Beauty Shop
404579.description: When her egotistical boss takes credit for her work, Gina leaves to open a shop of her own but her former boss will stop at nothing to shut her down.

404623.title: Battle Royale
404623.description: A group of students from a Japanese high school are forced to compete in a battle, killing one another until only one is left standing.

405451.title: Rescue Dawn
405451.description: Based on the true story of a captured German-American fighter pilot in the Vietnam War who plans a daring escape after suffering abuse by his captors.

405675.title: Thief
405675.description: A master safecracker plans his last heist for the sake of a woman but the gangster who hires him won't let go so easily in this tense drama.

407784.title: Alice
407784.description: A mousy, pampered woman who married well tries to find herself and contemplates the unthinkable--an extramarital affair.

02269.title: Eden of the East
02269.description: Akira Takizawa wakes up outside the White House with a phone that gives him access to ten billion yen and a woman who will grant any request. He doesn’t remember he’s supposed to save Japan. And he doesn’t remember that he’ll be killed if he fails.

02346.title: Original Popeye
02346.description: The spunky but lovable spinach-eating sailor stars alongside his friends and rivals to share his rousing adventures.
